OL,3,CPaul Brand explains which bills could
OL,4,Crise and what to do to keep costs down.
OL,6,FWatch Rising Bills: How Can You Save
OL,7,FMoney - Tonight on ITV1, 19:30
OL,9,FBritain's now been in a cost of living
OL,10,Fcrisis for nearly 5 years. Prices of
OL,11,Four daily essentials have been rising
OL,12,Fmuch faster than our average incomes,
OL,13,Fputting a damaging squeeze on our
OL,14,Ffinances. And now many of us are
OL,15,Fbracing ourselves for a fresh wave of
OL,16,Fprice rises.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
