CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779415426
OL,3,CPaul Brand explains which bills could
OL,4,Crise and what to do to keep costs down.
OL,6,F"In our latest survey of consumers,
OL,7,Ftwo thirds of households said they're
OL,8,Fmaking changes to their shopping and
OL,9,Feating habits to bring down costs.
OL,10,FThis is not just people being worried
OL,11,For overreacting, they're having to
OL,12,Fmake real changes to the essentials,
OL,13,Fnot just cutting out the luxuries."
OL,14,FSam Richardson, Which?
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
