OL,3,CPaul Brand explains which bills could
OL,4,Crise and what to do to keep costs down.
OL,6,FIn West Suffolk, we meet Bonnie and
OL,7,FSeb, parents of four who are trying to
OL,8,Freduce their household spending with
OL,9,Fthe help of personal finance expert
OL,10,FLynn Beattie, also known as "Mrs Mummy
OL,11,FPenny". With 4 kids to feed, Bonnie
OL,12,Falready batch cooks and they do keep a
OL,13,Fwatchful eye on their budget. But
OL,14,Frising bills are still making life
OL,15,Fharder.
OL,17,F"If we did have a bit of extra money
OL,18,Fsaved aside and we could do more
OL,19,Ffamily things on a weekend and enjoy
OL,20,Fit a bit more, have a bit more quality
OL,21,Fof life in that sense." - Bonnie
OL,26,@rD@]OUsD@FO]yD@AOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
