OL,3,CPaul Brand explains which bills could
OL,4,Crise and what to do to keep costs down.
OL,6,FLynn helps the family review their
OL,7,Fsubscriptions, grocery spending and
OL,8,Fhousehold bills, setting them a two-
OL,9,Fweek challenge to cut costs.
OL,11,F"So just be really critical about the
OL,12,Fcosts going through your account and
OL,13,Fthink, do I really need this? Can I
OL,14,Flive without it, yes or no?" - Lynn
OL,15,FBeattie
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
