OL,3,CPaul Brand explains which bills could
OL,4,Crise and what to do to keep costs down.
OL,6,FThe programme also investigates the
OL,7,Fimpact rising fuel prices are having
OL,8,Fon drivers and petrol stations. In
OL,9,FSouth East London, petrol station
OL,10,Fmanager Meera says higher prices at
OL,11,Fthe pumps has led to a drop in trade,
OL,12,Fand it's hitting her business hard.
OL,14,F"It's really stressful and really
OL,15,Funder pressure day to day. I didn't
OL,16,Ftake my wages for one month because I
OL,17,Fcan't, I don't have money because I
OL,18,Fneed to pay the staff salary." - Meera
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
