OL,3,CPaul Brand explains which bills could
OL,4,Crise and what to do to keep costs down.
OL,6,FA survey last week found more than a
OL,7,Fthird of UK households feel their
OL,8,Ffinances have worsened in the last 12
OL,9,Fmonths - with rising living costs
OL,10,Fbeing the main reason.
OL,12,F"We've already got people struggling
OL,13,Fwith energy, council tax, rent, etc.
OL,14,Fas well as their credit debts. So we
OL,15,Fexpect volumes of people coming for
OL,16,Fhelp to increase quite significantly."
OL,17,F- Vikki Brownridge, StepChange
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
